text: Andre Dickens (born 1974) is an American politician and nonprofit executive. He is the 61st Mayor of Atlanta, Georgia since 2022. He was a member of the Atlanta City Council from 2014 until 2022. ==References== Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:Living people Category:Mayors of Atlanta Category:1974 births Category:Georgia State University alumni Category:African-American politicians
